1. Danas je moj *nastup* u pozorištu. (Today is my performance at the theater.)
2. Posle dugog čekanja, konačno je došao taj *nastup*. (After a long wait, the performance finally arrived.)
3. Oni su ostvarili sjajan *nastup* na takmičenju. (They had a great performance at the competition.)
4. Naš *nastup* je bio otkazan zbog lošeg vremena. (Our performance was canceled due to bad weather.)
5. Moram da se pripremim za svoj *nastup* sutra ujutru. (I have to prepare for my performance tomorrow morning.)
6. *Nastup* ove grupe na festivalu je bio nezaboravan. (This group's performance at the festival was unforgettable.)
7. Nije mi bio prvi *nastup*, ali mi je svakako bio najveći. (It wasn't my first performance, but it was definitely my biggest one.)
8. Publika je bila oduševljena njihovim *nastupom*. (The audience was thrilled with their performance.)
9. Glumci su bili nervozni pred svoj *nastup*. (The actors were nervous before their performance.)
10. Naš *nastup* je trajao tri sata. (Our performance lasted for three hours.)